568
00:31:29,121 --> 00:31:30,956
Your future refers to your married life.

569
00:31:31,022 --> 00:31:33,024
You're the first girl
he has ever brought home.

570
00:31:33,091 --> 00:31:35,260
His mom would surely see you
as his fiancée.

571
00:31:35,894 --> 00:31:36,895
Fiancée?

572
00:31:37,462 --> 00:31:38,797
I'm sorry, I'm going home.

573
00:31:39,831 --> 00:31:41,767
Hey, knock it off.

574
00:31:41,833 --> 00:31:43,735
I'm just attending his birthday party.

575
00:31:43,802 --> 00:31:45,670
If we do this, there would be
a huge misunderstanding.

576
00:31:45,737 --> 00:31:46,671
I'm not going anymore.

577
00:31:47,806 --> 00:31:50,909
This is how it is with children
of business owners.

578
00:31:51,610 --> 00:31:53,979
Our parents sent us to Yingde University

579
00:31:54,045 --> 00:31:57,048
in order to prevent us from meeting
ordinary girls outside the school.

580
00:31:58,550 --> 00:31:59,985
It's the same with our families, too.

581
00:32:00,685 --> 00:32:03,555
If my parents find out that I'm secretly
dating girls who don't go to Yingde,

582
00:32:03,622 --> 00:32:05,557
there would definitely be
a family revolution.

583
00:32:06,591 --> 00:32:09,461
Our marriages have long been set
by our families as business strategies.

584
00:32:10,862 --> 00:32:12,097
Even more so for Ah Si.

585
00:32:12,764 --> 00:32:15,033
He's the only successor
of the Daoming Corporation.

586
00:32:15,767 --> 00:32:17,502
Just imagine how important his future is.

587
00:32:17,936 --> 00:32:19,004
A marriage of convenience?

588
00:32:19,070 --> 00:32:20,005
That's right.

589
00:32:20,405 --> 00:32:21,807
Every one of us is the same.

590
00:32:21,873 --> 00:32:23,775
Why do you think we love
having fun so much?

591
00:32:24,242 --> 00:32:26,611
It's because, in the end,
for our family's image,

592
00:32:26,678 --> 00:32:28,613
we might marry a girl we don't love.

593
00:32:29,815 --> 00:32:30,816
With that thought,

594
00:32:30,882 --> 00:32:32,584
we have to have fun
while we can now, of course.

595
00:32:32,651 --> 00:32:33,952
So,

596
00:32:34,019 --> 00:32:36,788
