607
00:33:30,308 --> 00:33:32,477
Ximen finally did something smart.

608
00:33:32,544 --> 00:33:33,912
Whatever makes you happy.

609
00:33:35,247 --> 00:33:36,681
You look like an heiress today.

610
00:33:37,148 --> 00:33:38,750
A fake heiress.

611
00:33:40,385 --> 00:33:41,253
A fake?

612
00:33:44,155 --> 00:33:45,156
Happy birthday.

613
00:33:45,223 --> 00:33:46,157
Thank you.

614
00:33:46,491 --> 00:33:47,759
Ah Si, happy birthday.

615
00:33:47,826 --> 00:33:48,960
Thanks.

616
00:33:51,296 --> 00:33:52,864
