617
00:33:52,931 --> 00:33:54,099
Open it and see.

618
00:33:54,799 --> 00:33:56,101
Why are you being so mysterious?

619
00:33:56,167 --> 00:33:57,903
Hello, Young Master Daoming Si.

620
00:33:57,969 --> 00:33:59,538
