as your birthday gift.

624
00:34:04,976 --> 00:34:06,044
The car is right outside.

625
00:34:06,111 --> 00:34:07,512
You can see it when you go out.

626
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:09,748
Thanks.

627
00:34:09,814 --> 00:34:10,815
Happy birthday.

628
00:34:11,783 --> 00:34:13,585
This should cost at least one million.

629
00:34:15,687 --> 00:34:16,688
How about you?

630
00:34:17,122 --> 00:34:18,290
I...

631
00:34:18,356 --> 00:34:19,524
Happy birthday.

632
00:34:20,058 --> 00:34:22,227
