and forgot my gift?

636
00:34:27,999 --> 00:34:30,435
I'm sorry. I just forgot.

637
00:34:31,036 --> 00:34:33,004
If apologizing is enough,
what do we need the police for?

638
00:34:33,271 --> 00:34:34,372
Stupid girl.

639
00:34:36,107 --> 00:34:37,842
Never mind. I'll introduce you to my mom.

640
00:34:38,510 --> 00:34:39,444
There's no need.

641
00:34:39,511 --> 00:34:41,546
