Your mom won't see me.

642
00:34:41,613 --> 00:34:43,748
What are you afraid of? I'm not
introducing you as my fiancee.

643
00:34:43,815 --> 00:34:45,283
-Let's go.
-Idiot. What are you saying?

644
00:34:45,350 --> 00:34:46,585
I don't want to go.

645
00:34:46,651 --> 00:34:48,420
-Just follow me.
-No.

646
00:34:48,486 --> 00:34:50,455
