659
00:35:34,432 --> 00:35:35,533
Miss.

660
00:35:35,600 --> 00:35:36,935
May I ask who you are?

661
00:35:38,703 --> 00:35:40,271
<i>She's Daoming Si's mom.</i>

662
00:35:40,639 --> 00:35:41,773
<i>How terrifying.</i>

663
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,141
<i>How suffocating.</i>

664
00:35:45,610 --> 00:35:47,178
I'm sorry, I...

665
