Ah Si.

671
00:36:08,900 --> 00:36:10,435
Did you hear me?

672
00:36:10,502 --> 00:36:11,536
Mom.

673
00:36:12,103 --> 00:36:14,172
She's a girl who's important to me.

674
00:36:22,180 --> 00:36:24,049
<i>Daoming Si, what are you saying?</i>

675
00:36:24,115 --> 00:36:25,917
<i>How can you say that to your mom?</i>

676
00:36:25,984 --> 00:36:27,819
<i>You must have lost your mind.</i>

677
00:36:27,886 --> 00:36:29,187
<i>You said such a thing</i>

678
00:36:29,254 --> 00:36:31,056
<i>in this situation.</i>

679
00:36:31,122 --> 00:36:32,791
<i>Have you ever thought about my position?</i>

680
00:36:32,857 --> 00:36:34,125
<i>My god.</i>

681
00:36:37,996 --> 00:36:38,997
Ah Si.

682
00:36:39,764 --> 00:36:43,068
Did you say that she's important to you?

683
00:36:43,702 --> 00:36:45,670
Do you know what that means?

684
00:36:47,238 --> 00:36:48,173
Yes, I do.

685
00:36:50,909 --> 00:36:52,110
Please wait a moment.

686
00:36:52,977 --> 00:36:54,212
Mrs. Daoming.

687
00:36:54,279 --> 00:36:56,481
She's our classmate in Yingde.

688
00:36:56,881 --> 00:36:58,650
She's our good friend as well.

689
00:36:58,717 --> 00:37:01,086
That's right. She's definitely
not some indecent girl.

690
00:37:01,419 --> 00:37:02,921
Shut up, you two.

691
00:37:03,555 --> 00:37:04,889
Indecent?

692
00:37:05,724 --> 00:37:07,892
I'm not asking you
about those vulgar things.

693
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:10,695
I just wanted to know if her background

694
00:37:11,296 --> 00:37:13,498
is a match for the Daoming family.

695
00:37:14,165 --> 00:37:15,266
-Sorry.
-Sorry.

696
00:37:19,537 --> 00:37:20,605
Miss.

697
00:37:20,672 --> 00:37:21,973
What's your name?

698
00:37:22,474 --> 00:37:23,541
I...

699
00:37:23,608 --> 00:37:24,676
My name is Shancai.

700
00:37:25,110 --> 00:37:26,611
Miss Shancai.

701
00:37:28,113 --> 00:37:30,615
What does your father do?

702
00:37:32,584 --> 00:37:34,152
My father is...

703
00:37:34,219 --> 00:37:35,253
Well...

704
00:37:36,488 --> 00:37:37,689
Well...

705
00:37:38,289 --> 00:37:40,558
The chairman of Muye Entertainment

706
00:37:41,893 --> 00:37:43,161
is her father.

707
00:37:44,162 --> 00:37:45,196
That's right.

708
00:37:45,263 --> 00:37:48,099
This group has a golf course,

709
00:37:48,166 --> 00:37:49,934
a forest bath, aromatherapy,

710
00:37:50,001 --> 00:37:52,737
and various natural forest leisure
and entertainment facilities.

711
00:37:52,804 --> 00:37:55,240
They got listed in the stock market
as a public company just recently.

712
00:37:55,306 --> 00:37:56,274
Haven't you heard of them?

713
00:37:57,709 --> 00:38:00,211
<i>Why are they telling lies
that can easily be found out?</i>

714
00:38:03,314 --> 00:38:04,315
Is that so?

715
00:38:05,016 --> 00:38:07,819
Then an heiress
with this kind of background

716
00:38:07,886 --> 00:38:10,121
should at least know how to play
one or two musical instruments.

717
00:38:12,724 --> 00:38:14,459
Which musical instruments do you know?

718
00:38:14,926 --> 00:38:16,027
Can you play the piano?

719
00:38:18,029 --> 00:38:21,232
Then let's ask her to play for us today

720
00:38:21,299 --> 00:38:22,433
in this special occasion.

721
00:38:22,500 --> 00:38:24,035
Mrs. Daoming,
she has matters to attend to,

722
00:38:24,102 --> 00:38:26,104
so I think I would have to...

723
00:38:26,805 --> 00:38:27,872
have to...

724
00:38:38,917 --> 00:38:40,118
Don't be shy.

725
00:38:40,451 --> 00:38:42,153
Play a song for us.

726
00:39:13,351 --> 00:39:15,220
Mrs. Daoming, please don't do this.

727
00:39:15,286 --> 00:39:18,356
If Miss Shancai did not have time
to prepare for this performance

728
00:39:18,423 --> 00:39:20,225
and embarrasses herself,

729
00:39:20,859 --> 00:39:22,327
isn't that too cruel?

730
00:39:23,461 --> 00:39:26,464
A girl who wants to be
the daughter-in-law of the Daoming family

731
00:39:26,531 --> 00:39:28,466
has to get into the social circle
sooner or later.

732
00:39:29,334 --> 00:39:32,036
If she doesn't even have
the guts to do this,

733
00:39:32,503 --> 00:39:34,138
what would she do then?

734
00:39:35,907 --> 00:39:38,576
Please start, Miss Shancai.

735
00:39:42,580 --> 00:39:45,116
<i>Daughter-in-law? Are you kidding?</i>

736
00:39:45,183 --> 00:39:47,218
<i>Even if the sky falls down,
that's not going to happen.</i>

737
00:39:47,285 --> 00:39:49,254
<i>This kind of woman is going
to be my mother-in-law?</i>

738
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,788
<i>Who are you kidding?</i>

739
00:40:33,531 --> 00:40:35,033
What a joke.

740
00:40:54,953 --> 00:40:57,288
A western philosopher once said,

741
00:40:58,423 --> 00:40:59,624
"Women,

742
00:40:59,991 --> 00:41:03,227
your gorgeous diamonds and shiny pearls

743
00:41:03,328 --> 00:41:06,331
give you delusions of being a queen.

744
00:41:07,198 --> 00:41:08,800
But you didn't notice

745
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:11,069
that there is only
the poison of pretension

746
00:41:11,135 --> 00:41:12,570
and the aroma of arrogance.

747
00:41:12,637 --> 00:41:15,206
The aroma which attracts
and also kills people.

748
00:41:16,207 --> 00:41:17,308
Women,

749
00:41:17,875 --> 00:41:19,978
when you pay homage to fortune,

750
00:41:20,511 --> 00:41:22,246
cheer to fame,

751
00:41:22,313 --> 00:41:24,182
and raise your arms to power,

752
00:41:25,016 --> 00:41:27,552
please don't ask that bird
who used to sing in the past.

753
00:41:28,686 --> 00:41:30,688
It has flown to a place no one knows

754
00:41:31,789 --> 00:41:34,993
because its voice has dried out,

755
00:41:36,260 --> 00:41:40,331
along with the doom of truth,
dignity, and pure souls."

756
00:41:57,281 --> 00:41:59,684
Does the value of a person lie

757
00:41:59,751 --> 00:42:02,020
in whether they can play the piano,

758
00:42:02,086 --> 00:42:04,288
in which family they were born,

759
00:42:04,355 --> 00:42:05,957
or what jewelry they are wearing?

760
00:42:07,325 --> 00:42:09,193
What's so special about
knowing how to play the piano?

761
00:42:09,861 --> 00:42:10,962
Let me tell you.

762
00:42:11,329 --> 00:42:12,797
This is the only song I can play.

763
00:42:13,231 --> 00:42:14,298
