764
00:42:23,207 --> 00:42:25,176
Happy birthday. I'll go now.

765
00:42:25,843 --> 00:42:26,778
Wait.

766
00:42:28,613 --> 00:42:29,580
Ah Si.

767
00:42:30,114 --> 00:42:31,716
Do you have any idea what you're doing?

768
00:42:32,717 --> 00:42:35,153
You don't know how to behave
according to your status.

769
00:42:36,154 --> 00:42:38,689
You even lied and told me
that she's the daughter of a chairman.

770
00:42:39,157 --> 00:42:40,324
You're way out of line.

771
00:42:40,391 --> 00:42:43,494
It's not important to me whether or not
she's the daughter of a chairman.

772
00:42:43,561 --> 00:42:44,462
Shut up!

773
00:42:45,963 --> 00:42:47,398
Stop talking nonsense.

774
00:42:48,332 --> 00:42:50,068
You're our only son.

775
00:42:51,035 --> 00:42:53,604
You're so enamored
with such a low-class girl.

776
00:42:53,938 --> 00:42:55,206
What should I tell your dad?

777
00:42:55,273 --> 00:42:56,607
It was love at first sight for me.

778
00:42:56,674 --> 00:42:57,942
I don't want other girls.

779
00:42:58,576 --> 00:42:59,644
She's the one I like.

780
00:43:02,346 --> 00:43:04,015
This joke has gone too far.

781
00:43:04,082 --> 00:43:05,883
Mrs. Daoming, please don't do this.

782
00:43:05,950 --> 00:43:06,884
We're not...

783
00:43:06,951 --> 00:43:08,152
This is a family matter.

784
00:43:08,386 --> 00:43:10,121
You don't have the right to interfere.

785
00:43:10,822 --> 00:43:11,689
Leave!

786
00:43:11,756 --> 00:43:13,024
Get out immediately.

787
00:43:16,027 --> 00:43:17,128
You want to rebel?

788
00:43:17,195 --> 00:43:18,429
Stop them!

789
00:43:22,366 --> 00:43:23,301
Mrs. Daoming.

790
00:43:23,367 --> 00:43:24,202
Get out of my way.

791
00:43:24,268 --> 00:43:25,436
Shancai.

792
00:43:25,503 --> 00:43:26,537
Your bag.

793
00:43:27,572 --> 00:43:28,739
Stop right there.

794
00:43:28,806 --> 00:43:30,208
I won't allow you to do this.

795
00:43:30,608 --> 00:43:31,876
That's an order!

796
00:43:48,693 --> 00:43:49,627
Thank you.

797
00:43:56,100 --> 00:43:57,368
You were good at playing the piano.

798
00:43:58,035 --> 00:43:59,270
How can you say that?

799
00:43:59,337 --> 00:44:00,872
Your mom wanted me
to play the piano earlier

800
00:44:00,938 --> 00:44:02,140
